G-CHAT-B3-DISPOSER (v9e)  MULTI-TOKEN Δ-CONTINUATION (ΣΔLL over payload window [2,8))
====================================================================================
Per candidate: under REAL E greedily decode 8 tokens = the model's own continuation g[0..8);
under ZEROED E (same npos, null content) teacher-force g and read each token's log-prob;
signal = Σ (log p_real(g_i) - log p_zero(g_i)) over i∈[2,8) (skip boilerplate positions 0-1).
Teacher-forced ΔLL on the model's OWN answer. Same O(1) inject→score→rewind plumbing.
Telemetry TAU=+inf. Registry Boulter-84/lobster-180/Headlam-179; M_target=42; greedy.

